headline: BIG MILESTONE IN THE "LITTLE APPLE:" CHIPOTLE OPENS ITS 4,000TH RESTAURANT, LOCATED IN MANHATTAN, KANSAS
summary: Chipotle Mexican Grill (NYSE: CMG) today announced the opening of its 4,000th restaurant, located in Manhattan, Kansas, known as the "Little Apple." To commemorate this achievement, Chipotle's executive leadership team and restaurant leaders will ring The Opening Bell® at The New York Stock Exchange today at 9:30 a.m. ET in the "Big Apple."
